<h1>See that Information? THAT'S YOURS! Get excited!!!! UwU</h1>
<p>If you see an error, edit your anime by clicking below.</p>


<h2>Name of Anime:</h2>
<%=animelist.name%><br>
<h2>Genre of Anime:</h2>
<%=animelist.genre%><br>
<h2>Type of Anime:</h2>
<%=animelist.classification%><br>

<label>Need to edit, delete, or add an anime? Click below:</label><br>
<% if animelist.user_id == current_user.id%>
<form action="/animelist/<%= animelist.id %>" method="post">
  <input id="hidden" type="hidden" name="_method" value="delete">
  <button style="width:175px; margin:10px; padding:5px; border-color:black; border-radius: 50%;" onclick="window.location.href ='/animelist/<%= animelist.id %>';">Delete Anime</button><br>
  </form><br>
<button style="width:175px; margin:10px; padding:5px; border-color:black; border-radius: 50%;" onclick="window.location.href ='/animelist/new';">Add an anime</button><br>
<button style="width:175px; margin:10px; padding:5px; border-color:black; border-radius: 50%;" onclick="window.location.href ='/animelist/<%= animelist.id %>/edit';">Edit Anime</button><br>
<%end%>